ta flows <action>Extract any story-specific requirements that the\n   234→    developer MUST follow</action>\n   235→    <action>Identify any architectural decisions that override previous patterns</action>\n   236→  </step>\n   237→\n   238→  <step n=\"4\" goal=\"Web research for latest technical specifics\">\n   239→    <critical>🌐 ENSURE LATEST TECH KNOWLEDGE - Prevent outdated implementations!</critical> **WEB INTELLIGENCE:** <action>Identify specific\n   240→    technical areas that require latest version knowledge:</action>\n   241→\n   242→    <!-- Check for libraries/frameworks mentioned in architecture -->\n   243→    <action>From architecture analysis, identify specific libraries, APIs, or\n   244→    frameworks</action>\n   245→    <action>For each critical technology, research latest stable version and key changes:\n   246→      - Latest API documentation and breaking changes\n   247→      - Security vulnerabilities or updates\n   248→      - Performance improvements or deprecations\n   249→      - Best practices for current version\n   250→    </action>\n   251→    **EXTERNAL CONTEXT INCLUSION:** <action>Include in story any critical latest information the developer needs:\n   252→      - Specific library versions and why chosen\n   253→      - API endpoints with parameters and authentication\n   254→      - Recent security patches or considerations\n   255→      - Performance optimization techniques\n   256→      - Migration considerations if upgrading\n   257→    </action>\n   258→  </step>\n   259→\n   260→  <step n=\"5\" goal=\"Create comprehensive story file\">\n   261→    <critical>📝 CREATE ULTIMATE STORY FILE - The developer's master implementation guide!</critical>\n   262→\n   263→    <action>Initialize from template.md:\n   264→    {default_output_file}</action>\n   265→    <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">story_header</template-output>\n   266→\n   267→    <!-- Story foundation from epics analysis -->\n   268→    <template-output\n   269→      file=\"{default_output_file}\">story_requirements</template-output>\n   270→\n   271→    <!-- Developer context section - MOST IMPORTANT PART -->\n   272→    <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">\n   273→    developer_context_section</template-output> **DEV AGENT GUARDRAILS:** <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">\n   274→    technical_requirements</template-output>\n   275→    <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">architecture_compliance</template-output>\n   276→    <template-output\n   277→      file=\"{default_output_file}\">library_framework_requirements</template-output>\n   278→    <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">\n   279→    file_structure_requirements</template-output>\n   280→    <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">testing_requirements</template-output>\n   281→\n   282→    <!-- Previous story intelligence -->\n   283→    <check\n   284→      if=\"previous story learnings available\">\n   285→      <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">previous_story_intelligence</template-output>\n   286→    </check>\n   287→\n   288→    <!-- Git intelligence -->\n   289→    <check\n   290→      if=\"git analysis completed\">\n   291→      <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">git_intelligence_summary</template-output>\n   292→    </check>\n   293→\n   294→    <!-- Latest technical specifics -->\n   295→    <check if=\"web research completed\">\n   296→      <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">latest_tech_information</template-output>\n   297→    </check>\n   298→\n   299→    <!-- Project context reference -->\n   300→    <template-output\n   301→      file=\"{default_output_file}\">project_context_reference</template-output>\n   302→\n   303→    <!-- Final status update -->\n   304→    <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">\n   305→    story_completion_status</template-output>\n   306→\n   307→    <!-- CRITICAL: Set status to ready-for-dev -->\n   308→  