{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_018TeXppoPY3cVjSqvPEP63o","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_014mAxMuTQehgY6FWgGH2wPN","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"### 2-2-observability-hook-enforcement — create-story (2026-03-20T05:50Z)","new_string":"### 2-2-observability-hook-enforcement — dev-story (2026-03-20T06:00Z)\n\n- **Pre-existing BATS failures:** 4 tests in `tests/integration/hooks.bats` (tests 28-31) fail on master — `hooks.json` format mismatch. Not caused by this story.\n- **`extractCoverageState` was incomplete:** Existing function didn't parse `runtime` section or `runtimeTarget` from sprint-state.json, even though Story 2.1 writes runtime data. Extended it — technically a bug fix for Story 2.1.\n- **Gap details limited in hook:** Hook directs users to run `codeharness analyze` instead of showing file/line details (Semgrep too slow for hook context).\n- **sprint-status.yaml not updated by agent** — updated manually by harness-run.\n\n### 2-2-observability-hook-enforcement — create-story (2026-03-20T05:50Z)"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":505,"cache_read_input_tokens":44107,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":505},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f7a66acd-0cc1-40de-a592-d59e75273c0b","uuid":"429ae300-6f1c-4f5a-957d-6af45204b212"}
