{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01HBxGTqGUGGLX1Eq6koQZJL","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01GBPzzXHkCfCfXcajCL3oqA","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"### 2-2-observability-hook-enforcement — code-review (2026-03-20T06:15Z)","new_string":"### 2-2-observability-hook-enforcement — verify (2026-03-20T06:10Z)\n\n- **AC 3 FAIL: `gapSummary` hardcoded as empty array** — `checkObservabilityCoverageGate()` never reads gap data from sprint-state.json or calls analyzer. The formatting code exists but has no data to display.\n- **No `codeharness analyze` CLI command** — block message references it but command doesn't exist.\n- **AC 1 and AC 2 PASS** — basic gate behavior works correctly.\n- **VictoriaLogs returned no events** — CLI doesn't emit OTEL data (expected for a tool that instruments other projects).\n- Returning to dev for AC 3 fix.\n\n### 2-2-observability-hook-enforcement — code-review (2026-03-20T06:15Z)"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":212,"cache_read_input_tokens":65577,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":212},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f7a66acd-0cc1-40de-a592-d59e75273c0b","uuid":"d605f3b6-f57a-4365-936d-19d4a35eff6c"}
