8→      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   299→      \"resolved\": false\n   300→    },\n   301→    {\n   302→      \"id\": \"migrated-13\",\n   303→      \"story\": \"2-1-verification-observability-check\",\n   304→      \"description\": \"**Import boundary violation (fixed):** `runtime-coverage.ts` initially imported from `../verify/types.js` directly. Fixed to use barrel import.\",\n   305→      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   306→      \"resolved\": false\n   307→    },\n   308→    {\n   309→      \"id\": \"migrated-14\",\n   310→      \"story\": \"2-1-verification-observability-check\",\n   311→      \"description\": \"**logEventCount is binary:** Set to 0 or 1 based on gap presence, not actual log event count. Parser only detects `[OBSERVABILITY GAP]` tag presence.\",\n   312→      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   313→      \"resolved\": false\n   314→    },\n   315→    {\n   316→      \"id\": \"migrated-15\",\n   317→      \"story\": \"2-1-verification-observability-check\",\n   318→      \"description\": \"**VerifyResult field additions are breaking:** All existing `VerifyResult` constructions needed updating (5 files). Optional fields with defaults would reduce churn.\",\n   319→      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   320→      \"resolved\": false\n   321→    },\n   322→    {\n   323→      \"id\": \"migrated-16\",\n   324→      \"story\": \"2-1-verification-observability-check\",\n   325→      \"description\": \"**Task 2.4 no-op:** No new config fields needed — existing `observabilityEndpoints.victoriaLogs` already sufficient.\",\n   326→      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   327→      \"resolved\": false\n   328→    },\n   329→    {\n   330→      \"id\": \"migrated-17\",\n   331→      \"story\": \"2-1-verification-observability-check\",\n   332→      \"description\": \"**HIGH: saveRuntimeCoverage was dead code** — never called from production, only tested. Runtime coverage would never persist to sprint-state.json. Fixed.\",\n   333→      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   334→      \"resolved\":